text: The Born Mountain is a small mountain in the district of Olten in Switzerland. The towns of Wangen bei Olten and Olten have land over this mountain. It is 719 m above sea level. == References == == Other websites == *https://oltentourismus.ch/de/entdecken_erleben/natur/naherholungsgebiete/born *https://www.routeyou.com/de-ch/location/view/48069085 Category:Mountains of Switzerland
title: Born Mountain
